{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/extras/battle.png?t=1608623377\" /><br><br><i><strong>Summary</strong></i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Vehicles</strong> - Use vehicles such as tanks and helicopters to destroy the enemy. <br></li><li><strong>Modifiable terrain</strong> - Construct or destroy terrain to your advantage. <br></li><li><strong>Fog of war</strong> - Out-maneuver your enemy by utilizing the fog of war. <br></li><li><strong>Unlocks</strong> -  Each kit has a variation with some new items that can be unlocked. Expand your arsenal by unlocking new weapons with increasing experience.<br></li><li><strong>Squads</strong> - Invite some friends and play as a squad in intense battles.<br></li><li><strong>Online or LAN</strong> - Host or join games on LAN or online.<br></li><li><strong>Bots</strong> - Play with humans or bots.<br></li><li><strong>Kits</strong> - Choose between 7 different kits, each holding 5 unique items with varying tactical purposes.<br></li><li><strong>Conquest</strong> - Capture flags and reduce the enemy team's tickets to zero to win the battle.<br></li><li><strong>Tactical Items</strong> - Use smoke-grenades and flash-bangs to distract enemies in close quarters firefights. Call in air strikes using laser target designation and radio.</li></ul><br>The game was built with organic, home-grown C++ code, OpenGL and a few open source libraries by a one-man team.<br><br>Though I have limited time for this, I try to update the game from time to time.<br><br>I've found that the best way to play this game is to play 1on1 or more with a few bots on each team. <br>If you try it alone you probably want to play with a few bots on your side versus many more bots.<br>Maintain control of the most flags so the enemy tickets will bleed out.<br><br>I have one server hosted in France, so if you live in Europe this should be okay, but you can always host your own LAN server.<br>To host a public server you need to port forward:<br>UDP Port 17112<br>TCP Port 17113<br><br>Discord server:<br>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1608623377","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/page.bg.jpg?t=1608623377","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1608623377","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1608623377","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This game contains combat and blood."},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/extras/battle.png?t=1608623377\" /><br><br><i><strong>Summary</strong></i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Vehicles</strong> - Use vehicles such as tanks and helicopters to destroy the enemy. <br></li><li><strong>Modifiable terrain</strong> - Construct or destroy terrain to your advantage. <br></li><li><strong>Fog of war</strong> - Out-maneuver your enemy by utilizing the fog of war. <br></li><li><strong>Unlocks</strong> -  Each kit has a variation with some new items that can be unlocked. Expand your arsenal by unlocking new weapons with increasing experience.<br></li><li><strong>Squads</strong> - Invite some friends and play as a squad in intense battles.<br></li><li><strong>Online or LAN</strong> - Host or join games on LAN or online.<br></li><li><strong>Bots</strong> - Play with humans or bots.<br></li><li><strong>Kits</strong> - Choose between 7 different kits, each holding 5 unique items with varying tactical purposes.<br></li><li><strong>Conquest</strong> - Capture flags and reduce the enemy team's tickets to zero to win the battle.<br></li><li><strong>Tactical Items</strong> - Use smoke-grenades and flash-bangs to distract enemies in close quarters firefights. Call in air strikes using laser target designation and radio.</li></ul><br>The game was built with organic, home-grown C++ code, OpenGL and a few open source libraries by a one-man team.<br><br>Though I have limited time for this, I try to update the game from time to time.<br><br>I've found that the best way to play this game is to play 1on1 or more with a few bots on each team. <br>If you try it alone you probably want to play with a few bots on your side versus many more bots.<br>Maintain control of the most flags so the enemy tickets will bleed out.<br><br>I have one server hosted in France, so if you live in Europe this should be okay, but you can always host your own LAN server.<br>To host a public server you need to port forward:<br>UDP Port 17112<br>TCP Port 17113<br><br>Discord server:<br>","developers":["kelkk"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765010/header.jpg?t=1608623377","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256815522,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256815522/movie480.mp4?t=1608619894","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256815522/movie_max.mp4?t=1608619894"},"name":"Strid Beta 2 Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com